         <div xml:id="kzz7yh-k86069"><!-- l4d22cl -->
            <head xml:id="kzz7yh-k86069-Hd1e101">Circa litteram</head>
            <p xml:id="kzz7yh-k86069-d1e103">
               <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>CIrca litteram <quote xml:id="kzz7yh-k86069-Qd1e107" source="http://scta.info/resource/pl-l4d22c1-d1e134@27-28">Peccata 
      origia<lb ed="#V" n="76" break="no"/>lia</quote>: non 
      significa<lb ed="#V" n="77" break="no"/>tur hoc peccatum originale in plurali: quia in 
      <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>eodem homine sint plura: sed quia multiplex in 
     <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>effectu inquantum corrumpit diuersas vires anime. <quote xml:id="kzz7yh-k86069-Qd1e119" source="http://scta.info/resource/pl-l4d22c1-d1e182@13-18">Mox 
      <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>omnium prosterneret in via vitiorum</quote>: idest cito nisi peniteat 
      <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>quia peccatum quod per penitentiam non difuit: mox suo 
      pon<lb ed="#V" n="82" break="no"/>dere ad aliud trahit. Ita reus et peccator constituitur vt 
      <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>ante fuerat: idest similiter: sed non tantum: vel refert hoc 
      <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>ad reatum pene damni: non seruus. Quidam dicunt 
      pe<lb ed="#V" n="85" break="no"/>nitentiam exteriorem et interiorem esse sacramentum: nec 
      <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>duo sacramenta: sed vnum: et isti bene dicunt: est enim 
      con<lb ed="#V" n="87" break="no"/>munis opinio et vera. 
   </p>
